) Ɔdɔ na ɔde yɛ ne biribiara. Enti ɔdɔ a yɛwɔ no, Onyankopɔn na ɔde ama yɛn. Sɛ wowɔ tumi a wode beyi ɔhaw ne ntɛnkyea afi hɔ a, anka worenyɛ? Ɔdɔ a wowɔ ma nnipa nti, sɛnea ɛte biara anka wobɛyɛ. Onyankopɔn nso ɛ? Ɔno mpo deɛ ɔwɔ tumi a ɔde bɛyɛ, na ɔdɔ yɛn nso, enti ɔkwan biara so, obeyi ɔhaw ne ntɛnkyea nyinaa afi hɔ. Onyankopɔn bɔhyɛ a yɛaka ho asɛm wɔ nhoma yi mfiase no, emu baako mpo rentɔ fam; ne nyinaa bɛba mu. Sɛ wuhu Onyankopɔn yiye a, ɛbɛboa wo ama woanya saa bɔhyɛ no mu gyidi kɛse. O
